com.jwetherell.augmented_reality.ui

Class Marker

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.jwetherell.augmented_reality.ui.Marker
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Comparable<Marker>
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    IconMarker

    public class Marker
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.Comparable<Marker>
    This class will represent a physical location and will calculate it's visibility and draw it's text and visual representation accordingly. This should be extended if you want to change the way a Marker is viewed. Note: This class assumes if two Markers have the same name, it is the same object.
    Author:
    Justin Wetherell
